enku","articleId":"e67ca101dc","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"52c8caeed5","type":"paragraph","text":"三、一九七六年六月施义之在公安局长座谈会上的讲话，《公安局长座谈会纪要（讨论稿）》（有些参加会议的代表抄回去传达了）。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e67ca101dc","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d5f00a9f5e","type":"paragraph","text":"对上述文件，予以撤销。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e67ca101dc","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"33ba6f346c","type":"paragraph","text":"此外，过去公安部发的文件、简报中，属于“两个否定”、“一个砸烂”、推行“三位一体”以及“反击右倾翻案风”等内容，一律废除。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e67ca101dc","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a17fcb96ec","type":"paragraph","text":"一九七九年一月二十七日","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e67ca101dc","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}